==腎毒性==
有研究认为上述[[中草药|中草药]]中所含马兜铃酸具有消炎[[抗菌药|抗菌]]作用并具有一定抗癌活性，但同时具有[[肾毒性|肾毒性]]會引起泌尿道上皮癌為每百萬[[核鹼基|核鹼基]](nucleobase/base)就有150個核鹼基[[突变|基因突變]]，馬兜鈴酸基因突變能力強度是現今已知最強的致癌物質。<ref>Poon et al. and Hoang et al.,"Genome-Wide Mutational Signatures of Aristolochic Acid and Its Application as a Screening Tool"[http://stm.sciencemag.org/gca?sendit.y=5&gca=scitransmed%3B5%2F197%2F197ra101&sendit=Get%20all%20checked%20abstract%28s%29]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }},[[科學轉化醫學期刊|Sci TM]],August 7, 2013; 5(197).</ref><ref>記者陳麗婷/台北報導,"致癌馬兜鈴酸 老鼠吃3天就傷害久遠"[http://udn.com/NEWS/HEALTH/HEA1/致癌馬兜鈴酸%20老鼠吃3天就傷害久遠-8083280.shtml],[[聯合晚報|聯合晚報]],2013.08.08-03:10 pm.</ref><ref>{{cite book | editor = C.P. Khare | title = Indian Herbal Remedies: Rational Western Therapy, Ayurvedic and Other Traditional Usage, Botany | url = https://archive.org/details/springer_10.1007-978-3-642-18659-2 | publisher = Springer | edition = 1 | ISBN = 978-3540010265|date=Jan 22, 2004}}</ref>由服用这类[[草药|草药]]导致的[[疾病|疾病]]在早期被称为“[[中草药肾病|中草药肾病]]”（Chinese herbs nephropathy，CHN），后来改称“[[马兜铃酸肾病|马兜铃酸肾病]]”（aristolochic acid nephropathy，AAN）。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Cosyns JP | title = Aristolochic acid and 'Chinese herbs nephropathy': a review of the evidence to date. | journal = Drug Saf. | year = 2003 | volume = 26 | issue = 1 | pages = 33-48 | doi = 10.2165/00002018-200326010-00004 | pmid = 12495362 | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12495362 | language = en | access-date = 2012-06-13 | archive-date = 2012-04-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120426005932/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12495362 | dead-url = no }}</ref>另有研究表明，马兜铃酸经[[人体|人体]][[代谢|代谢]]将成为一种具有[[遗传毒性|遗传毒性]]的[[突变原|突变原]]，并可引发[[癌症|癌症]]。<ref>{{cite journal | author = Arlt VM, Stiborova M, Schmeiser HH | title = Aristolochic acid as a probable human cancer hazard in herbal remedies: a review | journal = Mutagenesis | year = 2002 | volume = 17 | issue = 4 | pages = 265-277 | doi = 10.1093/mutage/17.4.265 | url = http://mutage.oxfordjournals.org/content/17/4/265.full.pdf+html | language = en }}</ref>[[美国食品药品监督管理局|美国食品药品监督管理局]]（FDA）在2001年向[[美国|美国]]市民发出有关警报。<ref>{{cite web
